data.description: Take a look at this beautiful home within walking distance to Blue Turtle Marina and Old Hickory Lake!  Recently updated with new lighting, hardware on doors and cabinets, faucets, and paint!  Additional storage has been added in the garage and will remain! This 3 bed, 3 bath home is conveniently located close to Nashville, shopping, dining, and more!  Buyer should also research Non-Owner occupied Short Term Rental opportunities!
